title: Pharmacy Prep Evaluation Exam Review Guide 2012 [tahir99] VRG.pd
description:
Reference Guide for Evaluating Exam Preparation and Review & Guide
Lecture series and a complete resourceful guide that covers key topics and high yield summaries to help students prepare the Canadian evaluating exams. It is concise textbook with in depth coverage of topics Biomedical Sciences, Pharmaceutical Sciences, Social, Behavioral, Administrative and Management, Pharmacy Practice, therapeutics and OTC drugs
